    {
      "type": "scene-heading",
      "content": "",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "INT. SUBTERRANEAN SERVER CATHEDRAL - PRE-DAWN"
        }
      ],
      "properties": {
        "sourceRange": {
          "lineStart": 9,
          "colStart": 1,
          "lineEnd": 9,
          "colEnd": 49
        },
        "sourceSyntax": "h2",
        "style": {
          "pageBreakBefore": true
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "content": "",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "A vault-sized chamber of humming machines glows in bands of cobalt and amber. Rows of cooling towers breathe like sleeping animals. Battery backup lights pulse in strict rhythm with the city load forecast."
        }
      ],
      "properties": {
        "sourceRange": {
          "lineStart": 11,
          "colStart": 1,
          "lineEnd": 13,
          "colEnd": 74
        },
        "sourceSyntax": "paragraph"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "character",
      "content": "DR. MIRA QUELL",
      "properties": {
        "keepWithNext": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "content": "(adjusting her headset)",
      "properties": {
        "keepWithNext": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "content": "",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "Archive cluster delta is replaying logs from six months ago. Every minute, the timestamp jumps forward and then snaps backward. Look at node thirty-one. It writes a clean state to mirror, then resurrects a deleted route table."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "\n\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "We prune it, it returns. We quarantine it, it routes around quarantine. We checksum it, the checksum agrees with the wrong version. We compare against cold storage, and cold storage now believes the same lie."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "\n\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "The map service is already drifting. Dispatch will think the bridges are open when they are lifting for freight."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "\n\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "Ambulances will route into maintenance tunnels. Freight will stack on side streets. Passenger trains will deadlock on opposite platforms. If this rolls into morning traffic, the city will grid itself into concrete."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "\n\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "I need deterministic recovery, not optimism. Give me a narrow rollback window and a staging slot that does not touch live dispatch. Then get me legal approval to bypass the normal release freeze."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "\n\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "I know what time it is. I know what signatures are required. I also know exactly what happens if we wait for the memo chain. We have one chance to cut a clean branch and land it before sunrise."
        }
      ],
      "properties": {
        "paginationContinuation": {
          "enabled": true,
          "markerAfterSplit": {
            "type": "more",
            "content": "(MORE)"
          },
          "markerBeforeContinuation": {
            "type": "character",
            "content": "DR. MIRA QUELL (CONT'D)",
            "properties": {
              "keepWithNext": true
            }
          },
          "markersBeforeContinuation": [
            {
              "type": "character",
              "content": "DR. MIRA QUELL (CONT'D)",
              "properties": {
                "keepWithNext": true
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "parenthetical",
              "content": "(adjusting her headset)"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "character",
      "content": "RHO",
      "properties": {
        "keepWithNext": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "parenthetical",
      "content": "(from the mezzanine)",
      "properties": {
        "keepWithNext": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "content": "",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "Staging slot is available. Legal is asleep. Sunrise is still indifferent."
        }
      ],
      "properties": {
        "paginationContinuation": {
          "enabled": true,
          "markerAfterSplit": {
            "type": "more",
            "content": "(MORE)"
          },
          "markerBeforeContinuation": {
            "type": "character",
            "content": "RHO (CONT'D)",
            "properties": {
              "keepWithNext": true
            }
          },
          "markersBeforeContinuation": [
            {
              "type": "character",
              "content": "RHO (CONT'D)",
              "properties": {
                "keepWithNext": true
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "parenthetical",
              "content": "(from the mezzanine)"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "action",
      "content": "",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": "A bank of monitors flickers and reveals a map of the city overlaid with thermal veins."
        }
      ],
      "properties": {
        "sourceRange": {
          "lineStart": 50,
